data.name: TextBoxDescription.Text
data.value:
UTMConnect is a one-stop platform where students can display and sell their products and services within a secure environment.
Welcome to UTMConnect! a platform that empowers student to showcase products and services.Designed with security and ease of use in mind, UTMConnect fosters connections between sellers and customers, making student ventures accessible to all.
It includes:
Admin Role: Platform management and oversight Seller Role: Product and service listings by students Customer Role: Easy browsing and purchasing options
